<item>
            <title>[SEC-1936] concurrency-control max-sessions cannot be set to -1</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-1936</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;According to the JavaDoc in ConcurrentSessionControlStrategy, maxSessions can be set to -1 to allow unlimited number of sessions, however, the Spring security XSD requires us to set a positiveInteger&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="42511">SEC-1936</key>
            <summary>concurrency-control max-sessions cannot be set to -1</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://jira.spring.io/images/icons/issuetypes/bug.png">Bug</type>
